<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>However, little is known about how online groups affect behavior independent of effects from the social network and the whole community, with only a few studies examining their lifecycle [44,85], their effect on social network formation [8,54], and how they facilitate political engagement [21,83] and dietary choice [56]. 
</code></pre></div></div>
